I was recently met with an alert from Signal Desktop
that it was now outdated (was 5 something) and I needed
to upgrade to continue; providing a link to click, which,
of course was only for Mac, Linux or Windows. So I updated
my ports tree and built net-im/signal-desktop: make; make deinstall &&
make install clean.

